         Personally, i have no complaints about the focus items.  I have Affliction efficiency 3 and affliction duration 3.  They simply OWN for soloing.  As far as end game raiding....the wizards got the true benefit with the improved damage 3 items.  Their ability to crit, and the natural benefit of a per nuke improvement is way above our improvement with the dot focus items.  In fact, most raids i use a mage summoned improved damage 3 item over my own focus items as it is often more efficient for me to nuke.</P><P>I am on the whole happy with out focus items, but i wish that more attention would be payed to our end game efficiency rather than improving our already amazing soloing capacity.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
