         Focus effects were done wrong</P><P>They should have been more like FT items, anyone can wear them and get some use but the higher level gear gives a greater effect.</P><P>So spell casting haste 1-3 might give you 10%, 20%, 30% instead of 20% across the board that only works on lvl X spells.</P><P>That way you could have items that are worth keeping throughout your career. The incentive is still there to get the better items but you're not discarding an otherwise useful piece of gear because the effect no longer works on any of your spells.</P><P></P><P>Narben the Gnome Gnecro<BR>Colleague of Sanctuary<BR>Luclin server<BR>"Find your own damn witty comment"<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
